\begin_inset Formula $V=V_{1}\oplus V_{2}$
\end_inset

, где 
\begin_inset Formula $V_{i}=\ker\ f_{i}(\varphi)$
\end_inset

, причем 
\begin_inset Formula $V_{i}$
\end_inset

