\left(\alpha_{1},\ldots,\alpha_{k}\right)\cdot\Gamma=\left(\sum_{i=1}^{k}\alpha_{i}\left(v_{1},v_{i}\right),\ldots,\sum_{i=1}^{k}\alpha_{i}\left(v_{n},v_{i}\right)\right)=\\
\left(\left(\sum_{i=1}^{k}\alpha_{i}\cdot v_{i},\ v_{1}\right),\ldots,\left(\sum_{i=1}^{k}\alpha_{i}\cdot v_{i},v_{n}\right)\right)=\left(0,\ldots,0\right)
\end{multline*}

\end_inset

Значит 
